{
  "id": "RAW_cb75a61c",
  "title": "使用 Gemini 3 Flash 构建：可随您扩展的尖端智能",
  "url": "https://blog.google/technology/developers/build-with-gemini-3-flash/",
  "date": "2025-12-17 18:19:43",
  "author": "Logan Kilpatrick",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"audio-player-tts\" data-component=\"uni-audio-player-tts\" uni-l10n=\"{\n       &quot;stop&quot;: &quot;Click to stop audio&quot;,\n       &quot;play&quot;: &quot;Click to play audio&quot;,\n       &quot;progress&quot;: &quot;Current audio progress minutes with seconds: [[progress]]&quot;,\n       &quot;duration&quot;: &quot;Duration of the audio minutes with seconds: [[duration]]&quot;,\n       &quot;settings&quot;: &quot;Click for settings&quot;,\n       &quot;timeText&quot;: &quot;[[duration]] minutes&quot;\n     }\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n      &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Audio TTS&quot;,\n      &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n     }\" data-tts-audios=\"[\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Umbriel&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_82952_umbriel_2025_12_17_18_24_27.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;},\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Gacrux&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_82952_gacrux_2025_12_17_18_25_40.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;}\n      ]\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n   <audio class=\"audio-player-tts__player\" title=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\">\n    <source src=\"https://blog.google/self.ttsaudio_set.first.tts_audio.url\" type=\"self.ttsaudio_set.first.tts_audio.file.file.mime_type\">\n    <p>Your browser does not support the audio element.</p>\n   </audio>\n   <div class=\"audio-player-tts__container\" aria-label=\"\">\n    <div class=\"audio-player-tts__content\">\n     <button class=\"audio-player-tts__preview-play\" aria-label=\"Click to play audio\">\n      <svg class=\"icon audio-player-tts__play-icon\">\n       <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20251215-1743#ttf-play-spark\"></use>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n     <div class=\"audio-player-tts__text-content\">\n      <br>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"audio-player-tts__console\">\n      <div class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-container\"></div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"az4gx\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today we’re introducing <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3-flash\">Gemini 3 Flash</a>, our latest model with frontier intelligence built for speed at a fraction of the cost. Building on 3 Pro’s strong multimodal, coding and agentic features, 3 Flash offers powerful performance at less than a quarter the cost of 3 Pro, along with higher rate limits. The new 3 Flash model surpasses 2.5 Pro across many benchmarks while delivering faster speeds. It also features our most <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/developers/gemini-3-pro-vision/\">advanced visual and spatial reasoning</a> and now offers <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/code-execution#images\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">code execution</a> to zoom, count and edit visual inputs.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"b7t5a\">Flash remains our most popular version, with 2 and 2.5 Flash processing trillions of tokens across hundreds of thousands of apps built by millions of developers. Our Flash models are truly built for developers, and with 3 Flash, you no longer need to compromise between speed and intelligence.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"c9l0f\">Gemini 3 Flash is rolling out to developers in the Gemini API via <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-3-flash-preview&amp;utm_source=the_keyword&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=g3flash-q4-25\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a>, <a href=\"https://antigravity.google/blog/gemini-3-flash-in-google-antigravity\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Antigravity</a>, <a href=\"https://developers.googleblog.com/gemini-3-flash-is-now-available-in-gemini-cli/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini CLI</a>, <a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/12/build-smarter-apps-with-gemini-3-flash.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Android Studio</a> and to enterprises via <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/ai-machine-learning/gemini-3-flash-for-enterprises\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"2tjfg\">Smarter, faster and ready for production at scale</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"8e5og\">Gemini 3 Flash delivers frontier-class performance on PhD-level reasoning and knowledge benchmarks like GPQA Diamond (90.4%) and Humanity’s Last Exam (33.7% without tools), rivaling much larger frontier models.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Gemini 3 Flash delivers frontier intelligence across top benchmarks.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"Gemini 3 Flash delivers frontier intelligence across top benchmarks.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini-3-flash_final_benchmark-table_light_25-12-17_final.gif\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"e9ak0\">Gemini 3 Flash delivers frontier intelligence across top benchmarks.</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\">Gemini 3 Flash is highly efficient without sacrificing intelligence, pushing the Pareto Frontier of performance and efficiency. It outperforms 2.5 Pro while being 3x faster (based on <a href=\"https://artificialanalysis.ai/models/gemini-3-flash-reasoning\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Artificial Analysis</a> benchmarking) at a fraction of the cost. Even with the lowest <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/thinking#thinking-levels\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">thinking level</a>, 3 Flash often outperforms previous versions with “high” thinking levels.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Gemini 3 Flash pushes the Pareto frontier on performance vs. cost and speed.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"Gemini 3 Flash pushes the Pareto frontier on performance vs. cost and speed.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini-3-flash_pareto-graph_dec17_final.gif\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"wj2l3\">Gemini 3 Flash pushes the Pareto frontier on performance vs. cost and speed.</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\">In the Gemini API and Vertex AI, Gemini 3 Flash is priced at $0.50/1M input tokens and $3/1M output tokens (audio input remains at $1/1M input tokens). It comes standard with context caching, allowing for 90% cost reductions in cases with repeated token use over certain thresholds. Similarly, 3 Flash is also available today with the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/batch-api\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Batch API</a>, allowing for 50% cost savings and much higher rate limits for asynchronous processing. For synchronous and near real-time use cases, Paid API customers also have access to production-ready rate limits.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ffiap\">Gemini 3 Flash in action</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5r2v0\">Gemini 3 Flash is now integrated into many of our products and early customers are enthusiastic about it. With each new Flash model, it’s exciting to see what new use cases are created.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bh0ol\"><b>For coding</b></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"998b\">Gemini 3 Flash has even better coding and agent capabilities over previous versions, enabling rapid, iterative development, outperforming 3 Pro's agentic coding skill (78% on SWE-bench Verified) but operating faster for quick iterations. Today, 3 Flash is rolling out to users in <a href=\"https://antigravity.google/blog/gemini-3-flash-in-google-antigravity\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Antigravity</a>, our new agentic development platform, to provide intelligent coding assistance that keeps pace with your train of thought.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"6\" thumbnail-alt=\"Gemini 3 Flash vs. 3 Pro demo\" video-id=\"oCFqZ0Ri6gg\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"oCFqZ0Ri6gg\" data-index-id=\"6\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/oCFqZ0Ri6gg/default.webp\" alt=\"Gemini 3 Flash vs. 3 Pro demo\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/oCFqZ0Ri6gg/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/oCFqZ0Ri6gg/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$670413342$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\"><b>For gaming</b></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"72rjp\">Gemini 3 Flash introduces powerful performance for game developers, offering superior video analysis and near real-time reasoning that outperforms previous 2.5 versions.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Ascrocade demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Astrocade Flash 3\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Astrocade_Flash_3.mp4\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" external-link=\"https://www.astrocade.com/\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://www.astrocade.com/\" alt=\"Ascrocade demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$670413342$--></a>\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://www.astrocade.com/\" alt=\"Ascrocade demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$670413342$--> <!--?lit$670413342$--><!--?lit$670413342$--> \n      <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Ascrocade demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Astrocade_Flash_3.mp4\">Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can</video></a><a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Astrocade_Flash_3.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!<!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"81i0v\">Astrocade is using 3 Flash for its agentic game creation engine, generating full game plans and executable code from a single prompt, quickly turning concepts into playable games. (Sequences shortened.)</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\">Beyond development, Gemini 3 Flash transforms the player experience. It allows <a href=\"http://latitude.io/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Latitude's</a> game creation engine to generate smarter characters and more realistic worlds, directly elevating gameplay.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-pull-quote content-style=\"pull\" quote=\"Gemini 3 Flash has allowed Latitude to deliver high-quality outputs at low costs for many complex tasks in our next generation AI game engine that was previously only possible from pro level models like Sonnet 4.5.\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" author-image-regular=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_2.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" author-image-retina=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_2.max-96x96.format-webp.webp\" author-name=\"Nick Walton\" author-role=\"CEO, Latitude\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"presentation\" class=\" uni-pull-quote uni-pull-quote--pull-style \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Pull Quote&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__wrapper\">\n     <p class=\" uni-pull-quote__text uni-pull-quote__text--long \"><!--?lit$670413342$-->Gemini 3 Flash has allowed Latitude to deliver high-quality outputs at low costs for many complex tasks in our next generation AI game engine that was previously only possible from pro level models like Sonnet 4.5.</p>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__author\">\n      <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n      <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n      <div class=\"authors-byline-container\">\n       <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n       <!---->\n       <div class=\"author-byline\">\n        <a class=\"author-byline__link author-byline__link--disabled\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$670413342$--><!--?lit$670413342$--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__image-container\">\n          <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (min-width: 601px) 50vw\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_2.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_2.max-48x48.format-webp.webp, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_2.max-96x96.format-webp.webp 2x\">\n         </div> \n         <!--?--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__info\">\n          <p class=\"author-byline__info-name uni-author-name\"><!--?lit$670413342$-->Nick Walton</p>\n          <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n          <div class=\"author-byline__info-title uni-author-info\">\n           <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n           CEO, Latitude\n          </div>\n         </div></a>\n       </div>\n       <!---->\n      </div>\n      <!--?-->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </section>\n  </uni-pull-quote>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\"><b>For deepfake detection</b></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"66ohi\"><a href=\"http://resemble.ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Resemble AI</a> is using Gemini 3 Flash to provide near real-time deepfake intelligence by instantly transforming complex forensic data into simple explanations. They discovered that 3 Flash offered 4x faster multimodal analysis compared to 2.5 Pro, processing raw technical outputs without hindering crucial workflows. You can learn more about this in their <a href=\"https://www.ai.google.dev/showcase/resembleai\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">case study</a>.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"Resemble AI demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Resemble AI Gemini Demo\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/resembleai_gemini_demo.mp4\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Resemble AI demo using Gemini 3 Flash\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/resembleai_gemini_demo.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/resembleai_gemini_demo.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"81i0v\">Resemble AI analyzes a viral deepfake, offering near real-time analysis on why the content is fabricated. (Sequences shortened.)</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"lkfcw\"><b>For document analysis</b></p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9ncvl\">Performance gains often come with a latency tradeoff, but Gemini 3 Flash proves that fast models can still handle the rigorous accuracy demands of the legal industry. With strong reasoning capabilities without sacrificing speed, it enables new levels of efficiency for complex document analysis for <a href=\"http://harvey.ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Harvey</a>, an AI company for law firms and professional service providers.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-pull-quote content-style=\"pull\" quote=\"Gemini 3 Flash has achieved a meaningful step up in reasoning, improving over 7% on Harvey's BigLaw Bench from its predecessor, Gemini 2.5 Flash. These quality improvements, combined with Flash's low latency, are impactful for high-volume legal tasks such as extracting defined terms and cross-references from contracts.\" section-header=\"Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you\" author-image-regular=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_3.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" author-image-retina=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_3.max-96x96.format-webp.webp\" author-name=\"Niko Grupen\" author-role=\"Head of Applied Research, Harvey\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"presentation\" class=\" uni-pull-quote uni-pull-quote--pull-style \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Pull Quote&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__wrapper\">\n     <p class=\" uni-pull-quote__text uni-pull-quote__text--long \"><!--?lit$670413342$-->Gemini 3 Flash has achieved a meaningful step up in reasoning, improving over 7% on Harvey's BigLaw Bench from its predecessor, Gemini 2.5 Flash. These quality improvements, combined with Flash's low latency, are impactful for high-volume legal tasks such as extracting defined terms and cross-references from contracts.</p>\n     <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n     <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__author\">\n      <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n      <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n      <div class=\"authors-byline-container\">\n       <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n       <!---->\n       <div class=\"author-byline\">\n        <a class=\"author-byline__link author-byline__link--disabled\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$670413342$--><!--?lit$670413342$--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__image-container\">\n          <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (min-width: 601px) 50vw\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_3.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_3.max-48x48.format-webp.webp, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Frame_3.max-96x96.format-webp.webp 2x\">\n         </div> \n         <!--?--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__info\">\n          <p class=\"author-byline__info-name uni-author-name\"><!--?lit$670413342$-->Niko Grupen</p>\n          <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n          <div class=\"author-byline__info-title uni-author-info\">\n           <!--?lit$670413342$-->\n           Head of Applied Research, Harvey\n          </div>\n         </div></a>\n       </div>\n       <!---->\n      </div>\n      <!--?-->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </section>\n  </uni-pull-quote>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build with Gemini 3 Flash, frontier intelligence that scales with you&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"wt7z1\">Get started with Gemini 3 Flash</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"3ljrp\">Gemini 3 Flash is available across many of our products, APIs and throughout the ecosystem. As you explore the Gemini 3 family, you have the option to use our new <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/logs\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">built-in API logs visualization dashboard</a> and send us model feedback directly through Google AI Studio. Additionally, since 3 Flash is a reasoning model, you will also need to make sure to <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/thought-signatures\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">circulate thoughts in the API</a> or use the new <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/interactions\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Interactions API</a>.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"41a23\">Here’s where you can access Gemini 3 Flash now:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"9vu4p\"><a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-3-flash-preview?utm_source=the_keyword&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=g3flash-q4-25\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a> and the <a href=\"http://ai.google.dev/gemini-api\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"146c5\"><a href=\"http://antigravity.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Antigravity</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"27d7d\"><a href=\"https://developers.googleblog.com/gemini-3-flash-is-now-available-in-gemini-cli/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini CLI</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"3u57c\"><a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/12/build-smarter-apps-with-gemini-3-flash.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Android Studio</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"6ufpu\"><a href=\"http://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio/multimodal\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a></li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bb1ud\">We are excited to put this model in your hands and see what you create with Gemini 3 Flash.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 推出 Gemini 3 Flash，这是一款快速、经济高效且功能强大的 AI 模型，专为规模化生产而设计，提供先进的多模态能力，并在各项基准测试中超越了以前的版本。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 推出 Gemini 3 Flash，这是一款快速、经济高效且功能强大的 AI 模型，专为规模化生产而设计，提供先进的多模态能力，并在各项基准测试中超越了以前的版本。",
  "summary": "本文宣布发布 Google 的 Gemini 3 Flash，这款新的 AI 模型旨在兼顾速度与成本效益，同时保持尖端智能。它在 Gemini 3 Pro 的多模态、自主智能和智能代理功能基础上，以极低的成本和更高的调用频率限制，提供了显著更快的性能。Gemini 3 Flash 在许多基准测试中超越了 Gemini 2.5 Pro，并包含了先进的视觉和空间推理能力以及新的代码执行功能。该模型通过 Google AI Studio、Gemini API、Google Antigravity、Gemini CLI、Android Studio 供开发者使用，并通过 Vertex AI 供企业使用。它在推理基准测试中表现出色，将性能和效率推向了帕累托前沿，并具有竞争力的价格，对于重复 token 使用和批量处理有大幅的成本降低。文章还强调了它在编码、游戏、深度伪造检测和文档分析方面的应用，展示了 Astrocade、Latitude、Resemble AI 和 Harvey 等合作伙伴的实际案例。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 以低于其前身（尤其是 Gemini 3 Pro 和 2.5 Pro）的成本和更高的速度提供尖端智能。",
      "explanation": "其设计优先考虑效率，使其适用于规模化生产，同时仍能提供先进的多模态、自主智能和智能代理功能，其强大的基准测试结果就是最好的例证。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型具有先进的视觉和空间推理能力，以及用于复杂视觉任务的新代码执行功能。",
      "explanation": "这使得能够对视觉输入进行详细分析和操作，为游戏和深度伪造检测等领域的 AI 应用开辟了新的可能性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 可通过各种 Google 平台（包括 Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI）广泛供开发者和企业使用。",
      "explanation": "这种广泛的可访问性旨在促进开发者高效地构建和部署 AI 应用，并辅以具有竞争力的定价和优化的使用选项，如上下文缓存和批量 API。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "今天，我们推出了 Gemini 3 Flash，这是我们最新的尖端智能模型，专为高速且极低成本而打造。",
    "新的 3 Flash 模型在许多基准测试中超越了 2.5 Pro，同时提供了更快的速度。",
    "Gemini 3 Flash 在不牺牲智能的情况下效率极高，将性能和效率推向了帕累托前沿。",
    "即使在最低的思考深度下，3 Flash 的表现也常常优于具有“高”思考深度的旧版本。",
    "Gemini 3 Flash 在编码和智能代理能力方面甚至优于以前的版本，支持快速、迭代的开发，其智能代理编码能力（SWE-bench 验证榜单上为 78%）优于 3 Pro，但操作速度更快，实现快速迭代。"
